==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unscrew
<hw>Un*screw"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>screw</ets>.]</ety> <def>To draw the screws from;
to loose from screws; to loosen or withdraw (anything, as a screw) by
turning it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unscrupulous</ent>⟦br⟧
